Table 2. Ligand conformations, coordination modes and structures of complexes 1–6.

| Complex | Conformation | Coordination mode | Structure                           |
|---------|--------------|--------------------|--------------------------------------|
| 1       | trans anti-anti | μ3-κ¹,κ¹,κ¹,κ¹ | 3D (8T2)                              |
| 2       | trans anti-anti | μ3-κ¹,κ¹,κ¹,κ¹ | 3D (8T2)                              |
| 3       | GAA-cis syn-syn | μ2-κ⁰,κ¹,κ¹,κ⁰ | 1D looped chain                       |
| 4       | AAA-trans anti-anti | μ3-κ¹,κ¹,κ¹,κ¹ | 2D (3,4L83)                           |
| 5       | AAAAA-trans syn-anti | μ2-κ¹,κ¹,κ⁰,κ⁰ | 1D quadruple-strained helical nanotube |
| 6       | GAAAA-cis anti-syn | μ3-κ¹,κ¹,κ⁰,κ¹ | 2D (sql)                              |
